<header class="bg-green-900 border-b border-amber-200/40 py-3 px-5 flex justify-between items-center shadow-lg">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="text-amber-200 text-2xl">♪</span>
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-200 tracking-widest font-serif">Mysic</h1>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-stone-50">
  <!-- ヒーローセクション -->
  <div class="relative h-[60vh] bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url(/top-background.jpg)">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green-950/60"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex items-center justify-center px-4">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">
          自分だけの音楽、
        </h1>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-8 drop-shadow-lg">
          世界に一つの<span class="text-amber-200">Mysic</span>。
        </h1>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <%= link_to "ログイン", new_user_session_path,
              class: "px-7 py-2.5 border border-amber-200/70 hover:bg-amber-200/20 text-amber-100 font-semibold rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide transition duration-300" %>
          <%= link_to "新規会員登録", new_user_registration_path,
              class: "px-7 py-2.5 bg-amber-200/90 hover:bg-amber-200 text-green-900 font-bold rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide shadow-lg transition duration-300" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5つのステップ -->
  <div class="max-w-md mx-auto px-5 py-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <p class="text-green-800/50 text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-green-900 border-b border-amber-300/60 pb-3 inline-block px-4">
        クリエイティブを支える5つのステップ
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm border border-stone-100">
        <span class="text-green-900 font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-5 shrink-0">1</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 text-sm">録音・加工・保存</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-0.5">歌声や演奏を録音・音声加工・保存</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm border border-stone-100">
        <span class="text-green-900 font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-5 shrink-0">2</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 text-sm">伴奏再生</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-0.5">YouTubeの伴奏に合わせてパフォーマンス</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm border border-stone-100">
        <span class="text-green-900 font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-5 shrink-0">3</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 text-sm">ミキシング</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-0.5">録音済音声と伴奏音源を合わせてタイミング調整・保存</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm border border-stone-100">
        <span class="text-green-900 font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-5 shrink-0">4</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 text-sm">簡易動画作成</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-0.5">ミキシング済み音声を動画化</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm border border-stone-100">
        <span class="text-green-900 font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-5 shrink-0">5</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 text-sm">投稿サポート</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-0.5">作成した動画をカンタンにYouTubeへ投稿</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <%= link_to "今すぐ始める", new_user_registration_path,
          class: "inline-block px-10 py-3 bg-green-900 hover:bg-green-800 text-amber-100 font-bold rounded-full shadow-md tracking-wide transition duration-300" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>